Subject: RE: [VB] Another Engine Question

In the 3 NEW VW Mexican engines I have disassembled there were NO gaskets
under the cylinders, maybe they forgot on these?  These had GREEN silicon
(or substance of some origin) under the cylinders.

Ronnie

ps. I have taken the heads off of 1 new VW Brazilian engine but failed to
look under the cylinders on it, but did notice that the heads on these are
cut like a type 4 (shallow) and will not work on any other VW engine and the
fins on the cylinders go almost to the top of the barrels, thus, no other VW
head will interchange on those!

